Cinematrix CommandList

/suggest [title]    — Add a movie to the watchlist. Fetches year, genre, and IMDB rating automatically. Announces to #movie-queue.
/vote [title]       — Upvote a movie. One vote per user; rejects duplicates.
/whats-next         — Show the top-voted unwatched movie.
/watched [title]    — Mark a movie as watched. Resets its vote count.
/rate [title] [1-5] — Rate a watched movie 1-5. One rating per user.
/top-rated          — List all watched movies ranked by average rating.
/history            — List all watched movies with dates and average scores.
/poll-top           — Run a 24-hour Discord poll on the 5 most-voted unwatched movies.
/poll-random        — Run a 24-hour Discord poll on 5 random unwatched movies.
/queue              — Show the full unwatched watchlist sorted by votes.
/info [title]       — Show a detailed embed for a movie (genre, plot, IMDB rating, poster).
/remove [title]     — Remove a movie you suggested from the watchlist.
